<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>You're Invited! ðŸŽ‰</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p><strong><%= @invited_by.display_name %></strong> has invited you to join <strong><%= @company.name %></strong> on Anonymous Feedback.</p>
      
      <p>Anonymous Feedback helps teams give and receive honest, constructive feedback in a safe, anonymous environment.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= @signup_url %>" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
      </div>
      
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 20px;">
        This invitation will expire in 7 days. If you have any questions, reach out to <%= @invited_by.display_name %>.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
